        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26617962/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26617962/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55990212/" class=" " title="魅影">魅影</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26617962">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">老来孤独者的独白，受谣言中伤多年有时抱怨起来不免有些絮絮叨叨，有精华可取，8分！</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-27 23:59</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                老来孤独者的独白，受谣言中伤多年有时抱怨起来不免有些絮絮叨叨，有精华可取，8分！
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







